These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, journalist, chef, analyst
1. the entrepreneur is on the left of the analyst##1
2. the journalist is on the right of the chef##1
3. the entrepreneur is on the right of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Job   | chef | journalist | entrepreneur | analyst |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, apple, plum, pineapple
1. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1
2. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
3. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Food   | peas | plum | apple | pineapple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower, azalea, aconite
1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Flower   | azalea | balloon-flower | bellflower | aconite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bolivar, prince, dannemann
1. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Cigar   | prince | aristoff | bolivar | dannemann |

