.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, basketball, swimming, soccer
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |  2   |  3  |  4  |
| Sport   | soccer | water-polo | basketball | swimming |

